column2: SELECT     m.XMM, m.ra_COSMOS_OPTICAL AS ra_cosmos, m.dec_COSMOS_OPTICAL AS dec_cosmos,     n.objid, n.distance,     o.ra AS ra_sdss, o.dec AS dec_sdss  FROM MyDB.MATCH_DB AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra_COSMOS_OPTICAL, m.dec_COSMOS_OPTICAL, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObj AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
